r\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/prepare/choose-school-college-university.html\">Choosing a school, college or university</a></h3>\n<p>The different kinds of schools, when to apply and other requirements</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"https://www.educanada.ca/index.aspx?lang=eng\" rel=\"external\">Learn about student life in Canada</a></h3>\n<p>Tips on applying for scholarships, living in Canada as an international student and more</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row well banded-topic row-no-gutters mrgn-tp-lg no-box-shadow brdr-0 gc-srvinfo\">\n<div class=\"container mrgn-bttm-lg\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-lg\">Apply for a study permit</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row mrgn-tp-lg wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-6 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit.html\">Get a study permit</a></h3>\n<p>Who can apply, how to apply, processing times and what to expect when you get to Canada</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-lg\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/graduate-student.html\">Study in Canada as a graduate student</a> <span class=\"label label-info\">New</span></h3>\n<p>How to get your master’s or doctoral degree in Canada, apply to come to Canada with your family, and get faster processing as a doctoral student</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-lg\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/prepare/minor-children.html\">Study in Canada as a minor child</a></h3>\n<p>Find out what is required for a minor child who is not a Canadian citizen or permanent resident to study in Canada</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"shadow mrgn-bttm-md hght-inhrt mrgn-tp-lg\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\"><span class=\"fas fa-graduation-cap\"></span>  Programs you might be interested in</h3>\n<ul class=\"small mrgn-lft-lg\">\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/fmc-student-pilot.html\">Study as a French-speaking student</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/ibx-measures.html\">Indigenous border mobility measures</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row banded-topic row-no-gutters gc-srvinfo panel panel-body brdr-0 no-box-shadow\">\n<div class=\"container mrgn-bttm-lg\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-lg\">Extend or update the conditions on your study permit</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row mrgn-tp-lg wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-6 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/extend-study-permit.html\">Extend your study permit or restore <br class=\"visible-lg\"/>\n your status</a></h3>\n<p>How to renew your study permit or restore your status</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-lg\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/study-permit/while-you-study/study-permit-conditions.html\">Your study permit conditions</a></h3>\n<p>Learn about your study permit conditions and keep your contact information up to date</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"grey mrgn-bttm-md hght-inhrt mrgn-tp-0\">\n<h3 class=\"mrgn-tp-0\"><span class=\"fas fa-info-circle\"></span>  Changing schools</h3>\n<p class=\"small\">As of November 8, 2024, you can no longer change schools on the same study permit. If you want to change schools, you need to get a new study permit by applying to extend your current one. <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/change-schools.html\">Learn more about changing schools</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsmediaplayer section\">\n<script>\n    function docReady(fn) {\n        // see if DOM is already available\n        if (document.readyState === \"complete\" || document.readyState === \"interactive\") {\n            // call on next available tick\n            setTimeout(fn, 1);\n        } else {\n            document.addEvent