=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/apply-new-temporary-resident-visa-within-canada.html\">Get a visitor visa to return to Canada</a></h3>\n<p>How and when a study permit holder should apply</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row wb-eqht-grd row-no-gutters\">\n<div class=\"position-relative mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-tp-sm col-md-12 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbase section\">\n<div class=\"brdr-bttm eqht-trgt\"><div class=\"d-flex row-no-gutters wb-eqht-grd grow\"><div class=\"col-xs-11 eqht-wdth-ign\"><h3 class=\"mrgn-bttm-md mrgn-rght-lg mrgn-tp-0\"><a class=\"no-undrln stretched-link full-width\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/travel-outside-canada.html\">Traveling outside Canada while you study</a></h3>\n<p>What you need to re-enter Canada as an International Student</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-flex align-self-center\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row banded-topic row-no-gutters gc-srvinfo panel panel-body brdr-0 no-box-shadow\">\n<div class=\"container mrgn-bttm-lg\">\n<div class=\"mwsbodytext text parbas